we include newlines when counting these lengths

this line is not longer than 80 chars
this one is, it's a pretty long line, definitely longer than 80 chars for sure, yes definitely longer than that.
this one is exactly 80 chars, no more and no less, yes no more and no less yep.
this one is exactly 81 chars, only one little char longer than the previous line

we expect to see only lines 4 and 6 in the output.
